<?xml version="1.0"?><eml:eml xmlns:eml="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" packageId="ybfan.18.5" scope="system" system="knb" xsi:schemaLocation="eml://ecoinformatics.org/eml-2.0.1 eml.xsd"><dataset scope="document"><title>台灣產殼斗科石櫟屬植物(Pasania)保育與應用研究--殼斗科的開花授粉</title><creator id="1164589900587" scope="document"><individualName><givenName>Yi-Bin</givenName><surName>Fan</surName></individualName><organizationName>TFRI</organizationName><positionName>Assistant Researcher</positionName><electronicMailAddress>ybfan@tfri.gov.tw</electronicMailAddress></creator><abstract><para>殼斗科植物是台灣闊葉林中最優勢的植物之一，也因此在森林保安、水土保持、甚至碳吸存等功能上均扮演重要角色；過往木材亦被利用為香菇栽培用材，許多種類更是製酒與酒瓶木栓不可或缺之來源；由於其濃密的樹冠，也是行道樹與庭園綠美化的極佳選擇；此外也有被普遍食用的種類(如板櫟)。在形態上殼斗柯植物是葇夷花序，應該是風媒花植物，但是開花的時候花很香，又有很多訪花昆蟲，但是這方面研究在台灣竟付闕如。本計畫目的在瞭解殼斗科植物的開花生物學與授粉生物學間之關係，以為植物育種、生態保育和解說教育之依據。</para></abstract><keywordSet><keyword>小西氏石櫟</keyword><keyword>后大埔石櫟</keyword><keyword>天然結實率</keyword><keyword>訪花昆蟲調查</keyword></keywordSet><intellectualRights><para>usage rights  belonging to TFRI</para></intellectualRights><coverage scope="document"><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Lienhuachi, Nantou</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>121.0</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>121.125</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>23.75</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>23.75</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><geographicCoverage scope="document"><geographicDescription>Liugui, Kaoshiung</geographicDescription><boundingCoordinates><westBoundingCoordinate>120.375</westBoundingCoordinate><eastBoundingCoordinate>120.5</eastBoundingCoordinate><northBoundingCoordinate>22.75</northBoundingCoordinate><southBoundingCoordinate>22.75</southBoundingCoordinate></boundingCoordinates></geographicCoverage><temporalCoverage scope="document"><singleDateTime><calendarDate>2007</calendarDate></singleDateTime></temporalCoverage></coverage><contact scope="document"><references>1164589900587</references></contact><methods><methodStep><description><section><title>天然結實率調查</title><para>在花尚未開花之前將花以塑膠牌標示，並計算小花數量，1個月以後調查花序上的幼果數，算出結實率。</para></section></description></methodStep><methodStep><description><section><title>訪花昆蟲調查</title><para>開花的季節至各個原生地(各分所)調查採集訪花昆蟲，首先以直徑42cm之捕蟲網捕捉訪花昆蟲，然後迅速放置容器內，帶回實驗室以顯微鏡觀察、並記錄訪花昆蟲的種類和數量．採集的昆蟲保存在75﹪的酒精、或冷凍室中，以便於日後研究鑑定。</para></section></description></methodStep></methods><project scope="document"><title>台灣產殼斗科石櫟屬植物(Pasania)保育與應用研究</title><personnel id="1168228479090" scope="document"><individualName><givenName>育斌</givenName><surName>鄭</surName></individualName><organizationName>TFRI</organizationName><positionName>Assistant Researcher</positionName><role>Metadata Provider</role></personnel></project><access authSystem="knb" order="denyFirst" scope="document"><allow><principal>public</principal><permission>read</permission></allow></access><dataTable id="1182322802007" scope="document"><entityName>小西氏石櫟訪花昆蟲調查</entityName><physical id="1182322799225" scope="document"><objectName>小西氏石櫟訪花昆蟲調查.csv</objectName><size unit="byte">2402</size><dataFormat><textFormat><numHeaderLines>1</numHeaderLines><recordDelimiter>#x0A</recordDelimiter><attributeOrientation>column</attributeOrientation><simpleDelimited><fieldDelimiter>,</fieldDelimiter></simpleDelimited></textFormat></dataFormat><distribution scope="document"><online><url function="download">ecogrid://knb/ybfan.19.1</url></online></distribution></physical><attributeList><attribute id="1182322802022" scope="document"><attributeName>種類</attributeName><attributeDefinition>昆蟲種類</attributeDefinition><measurementScale><nominal><nonNumericDomain><textDomain><definition>昆蟲種類</definition></textDomain></nonNumericDomain></nominal></measurementScale></attribute><attribute id="1182322802038" scope="document"><attributeName>目名</attributeName><attributeDefinition>昆蟲目名</attributeDefinition><measurementScale><nominal><no